            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Iup</abbr><ex>piter</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Σ<expan><abbr>abidas</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <lb n="3"/>Hutri <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im Lager gefunden. Z. 2 (Anfang): lesbar als Ligatur aus MAB (M nach links gedreht) oder ΣAB. (B): Gudea - Chirila: Z. 1: Iupp(iteri); AE 1988: Z. 1: I(ovi) &amp;lt;O=V&amp;gt;p(timo); Sanie: Z. 1: Iupp(iteri); ILD: Z. 1: Iupp(iter); Gudea - Chirila: Z. 2: Mabidas; Sanie: Z. 2: M(arcus) Abidas; Gudea - Chirila; AE 1988; ILD: Z. 2/3: Zeilenfall fehlt.</p>
            </div>
